      "created_at": "2022-12-21T09:09:01.326Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Here is a list of features</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Upload your own route<br>\nAnd continue it day after day<br>\nShow the route on the screen<br>\nShow speed and distance</li>\n<li>Show all data from app (average watts, average HR, target RPM)</li>\n<li>Play sounds in web browser</li>\n</ul>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/4/422f7b56e95926c2ce2b1fa5f233a92de23dddc9.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/422f7b56e95926c2ce2b1fa5f233a92de23dddc9\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/4/422f7b56e95926c2ce2b1fa5f233a92de23dddc9_2_690x418.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"9rvf1v5s4uqGIu6JpVDJA42AClr\" width=\"690\" height=\"418\" srcset=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/4/422f7b56e95926c2ce2b1fa5f233a92de23dddc9_2_690x418.jpeg, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/4/422f7b56e95926c2ce2b1fa5f233a92de23dddc9_2_1035x627.jpeg 1.5x, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/4/422f7b56e95926c2ce2b1fa5f233a92de23dddc9_2_1380x836.jpeg 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/4/422f7b56e95926c2ce2b1fa5f233a92de23dddc9_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">2466\u00d71496 554 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>So this upload your own route feature would allow you to upload a long route and remember where you finished the day before and continue on your route.  It would send these segments of your map to strava.</p>",
